ActNorthwest Territories Act
SubjectCommissioner's Land Transfer Order (Fort Smith, NWT)
PrecisOrder approving the transfer, in perpetuity, from the COMMISSIONER of the NORTHWEST TERRITORIES to the MINISTER OF ENVIRONMENT of the administration and control of the entire interest of the Crown of lots 497 and 498 situated in Fort Smith, Northwest Territories, for the purposes of the Parks Canada Agency. The order also approves the transfer, in perpetuity, from the MINISTER OF ENVIRONMENT to the COMMISSIONER of the NORTHWEST TERRITORIES, the administration and control of the entire interest in the public lands of lot 510-1 in Fort Smith, Northwest Territories.
